    <section id="second" class="container-fluid">
        <div class="mid">
            <h2><span class="lektore">IELTS</span> Speaking exam format</h2>
            <p>The Speaking component assesses the use of spoken English, and takes between 11 and 14 minutes to complete. Every test
            is recorded. The Speaking component is delivered in such a way that does not allow candidates to rehearse set responses
